rity-al-sadaqah","tag-gratitude-al-shukr","tag-manners-adab","tag-obedience-al-taah","tag-parents-walidayn","tag-prayer-al-salat","tag-revelation-al-wahiy","tag-sunnah","tag-alms-zakat"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-725","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":31940,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/10\/zakat-al-fitr-purification\/","url_meta":{"origin":27037,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Zakat al-Fitr as purification for misbehavior","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, obligated Zakat al-Fitr as purification of the fasting person from vain talk and misbehavior, as food for the poor. Whoever pays it before the Eid prayer, it is accepted as Zakat. Whoever pays it after the Eid\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31971,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/12\/three-salat-not-accepted\/","url_meta":{"origin":27037,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Sins: Prayer of three people will not be accepted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThere are three whose prayer will not rise even a hand span over their heads: an Imam who leads people in prayer who hate him, a wife who spends the night while her husband is displeased,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34505,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/10\/21\/haram-wealth-not-accepted\/","url_meta":{"origin":27037,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Haram: Unlawful wealth not accepted as charity","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 21, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever accumulates unlawful wealth and then gives it in charity, he will never be rewarded and the burden of sin will be upon him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn H\u0323ibba\u0304n 3367 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Arna\u2019ut \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38236,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2022\/09\/13\/haram-sadaqa\/","url_meta":{"origin":27037,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Haram: Charity from unlawful wealth not accepted","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 13, 2022","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Qasim ibn Mukhaymirah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever acquires wealth by sinning to serve his family, or give in charity, or spend in the way of Allah, then Allah will gather all of it together and cast it into Hell.\u201d Source: al-Zuhd\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34471,"url":"https:\/\/www.a